  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13079733/wine-selection-1200_edited.jpg" alt="Wine Packages" data-udi="umb://media/4a938fece7704312b5936108d9532d87" /><br />
<p><strong>Order one of our fantastic wine packages which will be waiting for you when you arrive at your chalet.</strong></p>
<p>For the wine connoisseurs amongst you, why not pre-book a box of superior wine and it will be waiting for you on arrival. Enjoy a nice glass of Malbec or Bordeaux in front of the fire after a hearty meal or indulge in a glass of Prosecco while sitting in the chalet hot tub! We also offer a delicious cheese board with Port.</p>
<p>Choose from a case of six red, white or mixed bottles of wine for £50 or a superior case for £70. If you would like to mix and match the individual bottles according to your preference, just call us and we can organise this. These wines are in addition to the chalet wine provided alongside your evening meal.</p>
<div class="data-grid">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 20px; width: 250px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
<tbody>
