<tr>
<td width="auto" height="20" align="center" valign="middle" style="background-color: #f26419; border-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px;"><a style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" href="https://my.inghams.co.uk/login" title="My Booking"><strong>Add a Wine Package to My Booking</strong></a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>Please note:</strong> Wine must be added to your booking before your departure - it is not possible to add a wine package onto your booking when in resort.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<div class="g12" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Cheese and Port Package<br />£40</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13079683/port-wine-offering.jpg" alt="Cheese &amp; Port" data-udi="umb://media/ee99a4a5535d416f8384f2bac1e3a684" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Your Cheese and Port package includes:</strong><br /><br />Selection of three local cheeses <br /><br />Bottle of Taylor's Late Bottled Vintage Port <br /><br /></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br />Red Wine Package<br />6 Bottles - £50</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><strong>Choose from the below Red Wine options:</strong><br /><br /><br />Gran Fabrica Gran Reserva 2012<br />Carinena, Spain<br /><br />Marquis de la Coronne 2017<br />Cotes du Rhone, France </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br />White Wine Package<br />6 Bottles - £50</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><strong>Choose from the below White Wine options:<br /><br /><br /></strong>Italia Pinot Grigio 2018 <br />Veneto, Italy <br /><br />The Last Stand Chardonnay 2018<br />Victoria, Australia <span><br /></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><br />Mixed Wine Case<br />6 bottles - £50</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><strong>Choose a mix of the Red/White wine packages plus the Rose and Prosecco listed below:<br /><br /></strong>Pasquieres Rose 2018<br />Languedoc Rousillon, France<br /><br />Prosecco Vaudano<br />Veneto, Italy<span><br /></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br />Superior Red Wine Package<br />6 bottles - £70</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Choose from the below Superior Red Wine options:</strong><br /><br /><br />Domaine Bousquet Malbec 2018 <br />Mendoza, Argentina <br /><br />Chateau Lacombe Noaillac 2015 <br />Bordeaux, France <br /><br /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br />Superior White Wine Packages<br />6 bottles - £70</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Choose from the below Superior White Wine options:</strong><br /><br /><br />Cloud Factory Sauvignon Blanc 2018 <br />Marlborough, New Zealand<br /><br />Buxy Cote Chalonnaise Chardonnay <br />2017 Burgundy, France</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><br /></p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><br />Superior Mixed Wine Case<br />6 bottles - £70</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Choose a mix of the Superior Red/White wine packages plus the Rose and Prosecco listed below:<br /><br /></strong>Mirabeau Pure Rose de Provence 2018 <br />Cotes du Provence, France</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Prosecco Bel Star N.V <br />Veneto, Italy</p>
</div>
